          <div class="section-content">
            <ul class="modern-list">
            
                <li>Develop and maintain robust web applications using modern technologies.</li>
                <li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams including designers, product managers, and other developers to define, design, and ship new features.</li>
                <li>Optimize application for maximum speed and scalability, ensuring technical feasibility of UI/UX designs.</li>
                <li>Lead frontend architecture, ensuring scalability, maintainability, and best practices.</li>
                <li>Ensure efficient collaboration with the design team, ensuring Figma designs align with frontend best practices:</li>
                <li>Optimize performance with lazy loading, code splitting, and minimizing re-renders.</li>
                <li>Advocate for consistent design tokens, spacing, and UI patterns to maximize reusability.</li>
                <li>Ensure high-quality development by following SDLC best practices, from planning to deployment and maintenance.</li>
            </ul>
