              <li> Familiarity with RESTful APIs and serverless APIs for backend integration</li>
              <li> Experience with Git, Webpack, Babel, and CI/CD pipelines</li>
              <li> Exposure to Leaflet.js or GIS technologies is a plus but not mandatory</li>
              <li> Strong understanding of the Software Development Lifecycle (SDLC) and best practices</li>
              <li> Strong communication and collaboration skills</li>
